text: Minucci is an Italian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Andrea Minucci (died 1572), Roman Catholic prelate who served as Archbishop of Zadar *Chieli Minucci (born 1958), American jazz guitarist *Joe Minucci (born 1981), American football player *Minuccio Minucci (1551–1604), Italian Roman Catholic priest *Ulpio Minucci (1917–2007), Italian composer Category:Italian-language surnames
